IFPREVERB OUT -1
  IFVAR STANDING = 1
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO OTHERS %P goes out through the swinging doors.
    MOVEGROUP 205
    AFFECT 205
    ECHO OTHGROUP %P comes out into the bazaar through some swinging doors.
    AFFECT 3176
