				RANDOM DUMMY1 1 6 0
				RANDOM DUMMY2 1 6 0
				EQUAL DUMMY3 DUMMY1
				ADD DUMMY3 DUMMY2
				STRCVT 0 DUMMY1
				STRCVT 1 DUMMY2
				STRCVT 2 DUMMY3
				ECHO ALL The dice come to rest, a %0 and a %1, for a total of %2.
				IFVAR DUMMY3 = FLAG3
				ECHO ALL The attendant smiles and says, "You win, %n."
				ECHO OTHERS The attendant puts %n's winnings on the table.
				ECHO PLAYER The attendant puts your winnings on the table.
				MULT DANBET 2
				NEWITEM 8 161 ADJ1=147
				SETITEMVAL 8 1 DANBET
				EQUAL DANBET 0
				EQUAL DANDICE 0
				EQUAL FLAG2 200
				ENDIF
				IFVAR DUMMY3 = 7
				ECHO ALL The attendant shakes his head and says, "Sorry, but you lose."
				EQUAL FLAG2 200
				ADD PVAL10 DANBET
				EQUAL DANBET 0
				EQUAL DANDICE 0
				ENDIF
				IFVAR DUMMY3 ! FLAG3
				IFVAR FLAG2 = 215
				ECHO ALL The attendant says, "Roll again, %n."
